  "title": "documentation: Missing some widget icons",
  "body": "Some widgets do not have a specific icon in the documentation, they are re-using other icons. Here is the list of icons to add:\n- [ ] hitsPerPageSelector\n- [ ] hierarchicalMenu\n- [ ] numericRefinementList\n- [ ] priceRanges\n\nI also do not understand the `hits` icon. This looks like a graph to me.\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/283419/11030263/42d729a4-86cd-11e5-9f22-973edd35b4a0.png).\n\ncc @Shipow \n",
